From 66ef04f0dfae4785dab1cbab05c44fd1d299a63d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 06:25:16 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Switch backend storage to libSQL (Turso-compatible) for free
 host deployment

- Replace better-sqlite3 with @libsql/client so the app can run against a free hosted Turso database instead of a local file, since most free hosts (Render, Replit Autoscale) don't persist local disk between restarts
- Falls back to a local file (file:<DATA_DIR>/chore-tracker.db) when TURSO_DATABASE_URL isn't set, so local dev needs no cloud account
- Convert all routes to async/await to match the async libSQL client API
- Add express-async-errors so a failed query returns a 500 instead of hanging the request
---
